    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/c0f855c83b77d78443fde1f302240b25.poster.avif?t=1763037541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/c0f855c83b77d78443fde1f302240b25.webm?t=1763037541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/c0f855c83b77d78443fde1f302240b25.mp4?t=1763037541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Batora: Lost Haven》是一款以选择为导向的等距视角动作冒险游戏，具有角色扮演元素与独特的二元系统，会影响战斗、剧情、对话、谜题与结局，让你思考究竟何谓牺牲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Batora: Lost Haven》中，玩家将穿梭在一系列各具特色的独特外星球，并发现在这个星系，道德不总是清楚明了，是非对错之间的界线细得残忍无情。发挥独特能力并将不同的战斗风格发挥到极致，来击败致命的敌人、解开复杂的谜题，并接受来自奇特外星居民的任务委托。你的每个选择都将形塑自己的旅程，并决定你将如何执行自己的最终任务，也就是... 让失去的家园恢复原状。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>命运的呼唤</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾薇儿失去所有家人后，学会成为一名生存者。她从未想像自己将有怎么样的未来。为了实现她的命运，她必须闯遍宇宙来揭开古老的秘密，并做出改变一生的决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/48b5a634377720d521a56bfa40b28c3e.poster.avif?t=1763037541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/48b5a634377720d521a56bfa40b28c3e.webm?t=1763037541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/48b5a634377720d521a56bfa40b28c3e.mp4?t=1763037541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多层次的战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在对抗各种可怕生物与外星敌人的激烈战斗中，运用太阳与月亮的两种能力以及你身体和心灵的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择自身的道路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多重结局下，你的选择将决定这个宇宙和其中居民的命运。为了唤回所爱之物，你愿意牺牲掉什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>考验你的头脑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在优美的谜题空间中解开复杂且非凡的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/2efd5fc33f694ed653474a7a91a2ac2b.poster.avif?t=1763037541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/2efd5fc33f694ed653474a7a91a2ac2b.webm?t=1763037541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506440/extras/2efd5fc33f694ed653474a7a91a2ac2b.mp4?t=1763037541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
